headline: Armada Hoffler Properties (AHH) Surpasses Q3 FFO and Revenue Estimates
summary: Armada Hoffler Properties (AHH) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of +11.54% and +1.78%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
